      #nprogress {

        position: fixed;
        z-index: 9999;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 1px;
      }

        display: block;
        position: absolute;
        right: 0px;
        width: 100px;
        height: 100%;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px #E85439, 0 0 5px #E85439;
        opacity: 1;
        -webkit-transform: rotate(3deg) translate(0px, -4px);
        -ms-transform: rotate(3deg) translate(0px, -4px);
        transform: rotate(3deg) translate(0px, -4px);
      }
      #nprogress .spinner {
        display: block;
        position: fixed;
        z-index: 1031;
        top: 15px;
        right: 15px;
      }

        width: 18px;
        height: 18px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        border: solid 2px transparent;
        border-top-color: #E85439;
        border-left-color: #E85439;

        position: absolute;
      }
      @-webkit-keyframes nprogress-spinner {
        0% {
          -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);
        }
        100% {
          -webkit-transform: rotate(360deg);
        }
      }
      @keyframes nprogress-spinner {
